<div class="post-footer">December 31st, 2010 |  Category: <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/copyleft/" title="View all posts in copyleft" rel="category tag">copyleft</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/copywrong/" title="View all posts in copywrong" rel="category tag">copywrong</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/free-culture/" title="View all posts in Free Culture" rel="category tag">Free Culture</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/sita-sings-the-blues/" title="View all posts in Sita Sings the Blues" rel="category tag">Sita Sings the Blues</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/the-interwebs/" title="View all posts in the interwebs" rel="category tag">the interwebs</a> | <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2010/12/31/correction-again-again/#comments" class="comments-link"  title="Comment on correction again, again">6 comments</a> </div>
